Context: The Concept Art for Entertainment program (G407) is a Postgraduate program offered by George Brown College. Interested individuals can attend an online information session by registering and providing their contact email address (jamore@georgebrown.ca). Application deadlines, college news, upcoming events, tours, and other information will be shared with those who sign up. The information session location is online, and attendees will receive a link 48 hours in advance. Additional contact information includes the phone number 416-415-2000 (voice) and TTY: 1-877-515-5559 for individuals with hearing impairments, as well as the email address ask.george@georgebrown.ca. The college encourages visitors to check their social media hub for more information. The content of this website is subject to change without notice and should not be considered a representation, offer, or warranty. Students are responsible for verifying George Brown College fee requirements.
